    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Conquer the universe </h2>In Grocket you fly through space with a rocket and try to get to the safe base.<br>Immerse yourself in an exciting and dangerous journey in space that challenges you and your concentration in its own way. <br>There are numerous space hazards such as obstacles, magnetic zones and wormholes, as well as lasers,<br>lurking by the wayside. You have to get control of time and solve numerous puzzles to continue this journey.<br>Break the laws of gravity and search for clues to the next stop on your journey.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Play with friends </h2>Compete with your friends for time and exclusive rewards. Compete against them in leaderboards and secure your victory.<br>Don't have your own computer? No problem, you can play together on one device and try to break the laws of physics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2>• Storymode, where you get to know the different kinds of challenges and unlock new mechanics in the game.<br><br>• Freeplay, where you try to survive random challenges and put your skills with the new mechanics to the test.<br>• Co-op (Local Multiplayer) [beta: more levels coming soon]<br>• Steam Leaderboard <br>• Steam Achievements<br>• Steam Stats<br>• Shop and Skins<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > About us </h2>This game is the first to be released on Steam.<br>If you want to support us, get the game.<br>It helps us a lot and contributes to further development. <br>We hope you enjoy it and have fun playing.<br>If you notice any bugs, please let us know.<br>We're trying to fix them as best we can.<br>We would be happy to receive feedback.<br><br><br>Have fun in the universe!",
